raud.\\\"\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fraud\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peatywon 100m breaststroke silver earlier in the week, narrowly failing to defend the title he won in Rio and Tokyo, andsubsequently tested positive for Covidbefore returning to swim the medley relay.\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2725, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0091135232480182e-15, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2733, \"end\": 2738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9498543091187112, \"rank\": 0.05279303402284345, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peatywon\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"the week\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"the title\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"Covidbefore\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2787}, {\"ngram\": \"the medley relay\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 29, he is by no means certain to carry on to Los Angeles in four years' time, but while dropping several hints towards retirement, says he will take time before deciding his immediate future.\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 3019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2873, \"end\": 2884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999835386008, \"rank\": 1.4768025836175963e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no means\", \"from\":